          <source>The following example constructs an <ph id="ph1">&lt;xref:System.Drawing.Image&gt;</ph> object from the file ColorBars2.bmp.</source>
        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="138" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>Then the code scales the red, green, and blue components of each pixel in the image.</source>
        </trans-unit>
